    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a charm\u2014perfect for everything from your morning commute to those fun weekend road trips! I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
