    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six and a 6-speed manual transmission. Key mechanical vulnerabilities have been addressed: the rear subframe is reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The powertrain retains its factory-rated urgency, aided by a responsive limited-slip differential and refreshed Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows light road-going patina, the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no rod bearing noise. This is a mechanically sorted example ready for spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
