    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly bridges the gap between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, accented by clean body lines and well-preserved trim, with only minor signs of careful use consistent with its history. Inside, the cabin remains a highlight; the upholstery is supple and free of tears, the carpets are pristine, and all electronic features\u2014including the climate control and infotainment system\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent multi-point inspection. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride with responsive handling and firm braking. This is an ideal choice for a buyer seeking a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with genuine pride of ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
