      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW M\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era. It features the S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a limited-slip variable M differential. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe inspection and reinforcement, along with a cooling system overhaul. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and balance expected of this chassis. A high-performance icon ready for the road.",
